Revision history for YAWF-Object-MongoDB

0.03    2013-02-18
        - Added grouping support for ->list
        - Added support for SERVER, DATABASE and COLLECTION class methods

0.02    2011-07-21
        - Fixed ->list option forwarding to MongoDB (SEWI)
        - Fix sort conversion bug, no [ ] unless neccessary (SEWI)
        - Fixed: Wrong database was being used if two databases with
          same collection names where accessed (SEWI)
        - Added tests for multiple databases (SEWI)
        - Re-order tests (SEWI)
        - Add a sort order test (SEWI)

0.01    2011-06-16
        First version, released on an unsuspecting world.
